tag_summary = "vBulletin is prone to multiple cross-site scripting vulnerabilities
because it fails to properly sanitize user-supplied input.

An attacker may leverage these issues to execute arbitrary script code
in the browser of an unsuspecting user in the context of the affected
site. This may let the attacker steal cookie-based authentication
credentials and launch other attacks.

vBulletin versions prior to 4.0.2 PL4 are vulnerable.";

tag_solution = "The vendor released updates to address these issues. Please see the
references for more information.";

